title: Don't Be Donkey Go Vote
itunes:title: Don't Be Donkey Go Vote
description:
Tuesday 11/06 - Today on the show we had Michelle Williams and her fiance Chad Johnson stop by where they spoke about depression, not having sex before marriage and more. Also, did you vote today? well if you didn't you are Donkey of the Day today, as Charlamagne gave the hee-haw to all the non voters today, but we also wanted to know why some are not voting, so we opened up the phone lines to hear their reasoning.
